## Common Mistakes to Avoid

1. ❌ **Hardcoding colors** - Always use design tokens
2. ❌ **Missing dark mode** - Always include `dark:` variants
3. ❌ **Inconsistent spacing** - Use 4px base scale
4. ❌ **Creating duplicate components** - Check existing components first
5. ❌ **Missing accessibility** - Always include ARIA and keyboard support
6. ❌ **Custom glassmorphism** - Use the `glassmorphic` utility class
7. ❌ **Not using cn()** - Always use `cn()` for className merging

